<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>١٣٧ - <span class="c2">(٤٤٢)</span> حَدَّثَنَا<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>⦗٣٣⦘<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span> <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/5774">ابْنُ نُمَيْرٍ </a>، حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3955">أَبِي </a>، حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/1681">حَنْظَلَةُ </a>قَالَ: سَمِعْتُ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2249">سَالِمًا </a>يَقُولُ: سَمِعْتُ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3807">ابْنَ عُمَرَ </a>يَقُولُ: سَمِعْتُ رَسُولَ اللهِ <span class="special">ﷺ</span> يَقُولُ: <span class="c2">« إِذَا اسْتَأْذَنَكُمْ نِسَاؤُكُمْ إِلَى الْمَسَاجِدِ فَأْذَنُوا لَهُنَّ »</span>.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>